Helloaf friends!! We’re sorry for going MIA on you for a while there. Our parentals abandoned us at Grandma’s while they jetted off to Hong Kong and China for a two week vacay. 😫 While they were in HK, they played with our handsome Frenchie cousin @thatseblife and they saw three corgis! Finally when they arrived at HK airport to return home to us, a couple ladies looked at my parentals and exclaimed, “YOU’RE RALPH AND GEORGE’S MOM AND DAD!!” They had recognized Broham and Seester, as they’ve following our account since back in the day when Broham was born! It’s a small corgi loving world! Swipe to see some of their trip and Mahm will be posting more about the trip over at @loavesandlittles. Also, thanks fur all the messages of concern while we were gone; we felt the loaf and we’re so glad to be back with you! #MuchLoaf
